name: Geekbench: Text Processing
description: Loads 190 markdown files, parses the contents using regular expressions, stores metadata in a SQLite database, and exports the content to a different format on an in-memory encrypted file system, using a mix of C++ and Python.The score is calibrated against a baseline score of 2,500 (Dell Precision 3460 with a Core i7-12700 processor) as per the Geekbench 6 Benchmark Internals.
